Funtions:is a block of code to perform perticular task
		ex add()-->10+20 -->30
types of funtions:
		-->user defined 
					-->4 types based on arguments and return values
						-->funtion with out arguments and with out return value
						-->Funiton with out arguments and with return value
						-->funtion with arguments and with out return value
						-->funtion with arguments and with return value
		-->pre defined
				-->ex scanf(),printf(),pow(),strlen(),strcpy(),clrscr(),getc(),gets(),fscanf(),fprintf() ect..
Funtion parts:
			-->Funtion Declaration
			-->Funtion Defination
			-->Funtion calling
uses:
		-->Re useability
		-->Error finding easy
		-->Code length reduces
			
			
			
			
